question: 所載
sourceMnemonic: The item is in a <kanji>place</kanji> in its existence where it is <kanji>publish</kanji>ed. If something is in this place, it is <vocabulary>printed</vocabulary> and <vocabulary>published</vocabulary>.
sourceReadingMnemonic: This is a jukugo word, which usually means on'yomi readings from the kanji. If you know the readings of your kanji you'll know how to read this as well.
